<chapter xml:id="Tuning">
  <title>Tuning</title>
  <para>
    This chapter contains some tricks you may use to optimize the performance
    of your LIXA installation.
  </para>
  <section>
    <title>Overview</title>
    <para>
      There are basically 3 factors you can tune in your LIXA installation:
      number of server threads, min and max elapsed synchronization time,
      state file disk assignment.
    </para>
